title: MisterMusic Show 371 -indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 371 - [2 hours] 192 kbps MP3 stereo-


MisterMusic has new tunes on the show this week from Metric, and Albert Hammond Jr.
Plus a big alternative rock hit from September 1995 is the 'Oldie of the Week'.
A song that provided the first entry on the American top 40 billboard chart for this band. It also was number one for 2 weeks on the modern rock chart.



The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
